		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about the band.  For the Smiths' self-titled debut album, see <a href="/wiki/The_Smiths_(album)" title="The Smiths (album)">The Smiths (album)</a>.</div>
