<p><a name="Notes" id="Notes"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Smiths&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes</span></h2>
